{{Infobox dungeon |name = Sea Spirit's Den |image = [[File:Sea Spirit's Den.png|250px]] |caption = A map of Sea Spirit's Den. |tokens = 725,000 |location = East of Azure Bay. }} '''Sea Spirit's Den''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Kalos]]. It initially has 100 tiles arranged in a 10x10 square, including 10 chest tiles, 23 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 7,543,000 HP.
